al race\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1615}, {\"ngram\": \"breaststroke\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1631}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1641, \"to\": 1649}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1686, \"to\": 1693}, {\"ngram\": \"a chaperone\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1717}, {\"ngram\": \"the chaperone\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1735}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Pulled her out of the pool, put her bathrobe on.\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1807, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1785}, {\"ngram\": \"her bathrobe\", \"from\": 1791, \"to\": 1803}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was actually the first female swimmer to win a gold medal in swimming for Great Britain.\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1900, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1886, \"end\": 1899, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9532801938089152, \"rank\": 0.048761250132106, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first female swimmer\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1849}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold medal\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 1869}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am really proud of her.\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 1928, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At that age, that time, females were not doing anything like that and to have actually swam at the age of 27, I think it was quite old back then.\\\"\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 2075, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that age\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 1940}, {\"ngram\": \"females\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 1960}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1976, \"to\": 1984}, {\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2031}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2186, \"entities\": 